vīryapāramitā tu kuśalotsāhasvabhāvātivispaṣṭaṃ cittam evety āha. vacanakāyasahitasyāpi cittasya kuśalapakṣe mandapracārasya na tādṛśaṃ phalamupajāyate, yādṛśaṃ dhyānādiviṣaye paṭupravṛtter ekākino 'pi cittasya phalaṃ brahmabhūyādikam. tasmāt sā cittam eva.

<commentary>dhyānaṃ tu cittaikāgratālakṣaṇaṃ cittādanyathā vaktumaśakyamity āha-

mantrādyāvartanalakṣaṇā vacanavyāpārā japāḥ. tapāṃsi ca indriyadamanalakṣaṇāḥ kāyikāḥ. tāny atibahukālam abhyastāny apy anyatra saktacittena middhādyupahatacittena vā, samānapāṭavavikalenety arthaḥ, vṛthaiva niṣphalam eva, atyarthakṛśaphalatvāt, abhimatārthe 'nupayogād vā. putro 'py aputra eva, putrakāryākaraṇād yathā. ity āha bhagavān sarvajñaḥ. tasmād dhyānapāramitāpi cittam eva.</commentary>

prajñā tu nirvivādā cittam evety āha. pañcagatisaṃsārajātyādiduḥkhaṃ prahātuṃ tatprahāṇe nirvāṇasukham adhigantuṃ te sattvā mudhā nirarthakā eva bhramanty ambare kāsīpuṣpam iva niṣphalaṃ saṃsāre.